<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/9(Thu.)25 Ways to Be a Happier Person/7 communication skills to succeed in the workplace(Host:Cammy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=279&amp;p=295#p295"><![CDATA[
Session I: 25 Scientifically Proven Ways to Be a Happier Person<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.health.com/health/gallery/0,,20978719,00.html">https://www.health.com/health/gallery/0 ... 19,00.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />Q1: How do you help your friends when they are sad or frustrated? Please share your <br />experience or suggestions with your team members.<br />Q2: This article provides some food, exercise and tips that make one a happier <br />person. Which one do you want to try? Why?<br />Q3: How do you manage your work-life balance and become a happier person? <br />Please share your comments at your table.<br />Q4: Please share some happy things with your team members.<br /><br />Session II: 7 communication skills you need to succeed in the workplace<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90313078/the-importance-of-these-7-communication-skills">https://www.fastcompany.com/90313078/th ... ion-skills</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />Q1: What's your thoughts about a good/poor communicator? Please share some <br />stories that you encountered at work or home with your team members.<br />Q2: How do you master effective communication skills? Please share your <br />experiences at your table. <br />Q3: In this article, please pick up 3 communication skills and will practice in your <br />daily life.  <br /><br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. first topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:20 p.m. Presentation <br />8:20 p.m.-- 8:40 p.m. Sharing time : articles &amp; other experiences. <br />8:40 p.m--9.:15 p.m. second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m. -- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第一區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Sun May 05, 2019 12:09 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
